rComments: One of the worst professors I have ever had & actually inspired me to create an account here. She expected way too much of her students & wasn't willing to work with the students when they needed it. She would blame students for failing a test even though the entire class would fail. She didn't actually teach anything. I enjoyed Spanish before her.

She is a good Spanish prof. She is a fairly hard marker and she is generally well organized and clear in her explanations. If you come to class, pay attention, participate and make an effort to do homework/assignments you should be fine. Some classes can be very boring and repetitive.
She's definitely a cutie. Really helpful and easy on those who aren't really good in spanish. If you want to learn spanish I would say she's pretty good.
